 The November Biomechanical Studio was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 07 November 2021, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, on his date of birth.

  A vernacular biomechanical studio design uses local forms of creation that are derived from the surrounding region, adapting unique indigenous materials & advanced organism design. These design philosophies and practices have sustained the passage of space & time, a new definition of common sense and beyond practicality.   Ergonomically superior design to support your 24/7 Chaotic Beauty Lifestyle.
